Package StudentRecords

Class StudentRecords

java.lang.Object
StudentRecords.StudentRecords
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class StudentRecords
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
StudentRecords is an entity class which stores the information of a course taken by a student, and the student's identity informations.

Each entry has 11 pieces of informations, as described below:

key: identifies the student who takes the course

firstName of student

lastName of student

matricNum of student

indexNum: eg 10088

courseIndex: eg CZ1003

AU: number of AU of the course

courseType: eg. LEC/TUT/LAB

SU: SU option

GERType: eg CORE

status: REGISTERED/WAITLIST

queue of the course

Author:
Aaron Tay Han Yen
